Paragraph Explaining Purpose

The Study Buddy Web App is designed to help students organize their learning more effectively. 
It allows users to create digital notes and automatically generate flashcards from them for quick revision.
The app also includes a quiz mode, turning study sessions into an interactive experience. By combining notes, 
flashcards, and quizzes in one lightweight platform, the application encourages active recall and spaced repetition
â€” two proven techniques to improve memory retention. This makes studying more engaging, efficient, and accessible for students of all levels.
